						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass9FD225D22B9A45568CD94BF1734A73F8"><h3>
      <strong>Get help&#160;paying your rent</strong><br></h3><p></p><ul><li><span style="font-size&#58;17.3333px;">Call or text​ 2-1-1 for assistance</span></li><li><span style="font-size&#58;17.3333px;">Visit&#160;<a href="https&#58;//211info.org/" target="_blank">https&#58;//211info.org​</a></span></li><li><a href="https&#58;//caporegon.org/who-we-are/the-community-action-network/" title="link&#58; local community action agency" target="_blank" style="font-family&#58;&quot;segoe ui&quot;, segoe, tahoma, helvetica, arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size&#58;17.3333px;">Contact your local community action agency</span></a></li><li><a href="/OHA/HSD/OHP/Pages/Housing.aspx" target="_blank"><span style="font-size&#58;17.3333px;">​Oregon Health Plan (OHP) Housing Benefits​​</span></a><div><br></div><br></li></ul><p></p></div>
						</div>
